item.title: Places {317}
item.dc:creator: @WestSideMass WestSideMass
item.description:
@WestSideMass wrote:

The first thing you need is a command to take you to your staff zone. Simply add this code into your Client.Java file, and adjust the coordinates to your staff zone’s coordinates.

if (command.startsWith("staffzone") && playerRights >= 1){ toX = ####; toY = ####; sM("Welcome to the Staff Zone."); }

Add next to "toX = " the X coordinate of your Staff Zone, and next to "toY = " the Y coordinate of your Staff Zone.

Save + Compile. Go on your server, and type in ::staffzone, and congratulations, you have a Staff Zone.

If you have any problems, feel free to ask.
